"; Poetry corpus + form-as-meaning
; Written 2026-07-13
;
; Form-as-meaning doctrine (from durable memory):
;   - sonnet volta = Peirce abduction + Jung individuation
;   - haiku = Tractatus shown-not-said + Peirce index
;   - ghazal radif = Lacan absent-Beloved + Freud repetition
;   - blues AAB = Peirce anchor+inference + Jung shadow
;
; Rule: philosopher names appear in ANALYSIS FRAMES only. Never in the runtime's
; speaking voice. Public-domain / Waley translations for Japanese.

